{"word":"G568 - ἀπέχω - apéchō - ap-ekh'-o - Be","slug":"G568","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apéchō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ekh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03C9; - apecho&#x0304;</b> - <i>ap-ekh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192\">G2192</a>; (active) to <i>have out</i>, that is, <i>receive in full</i>; (intransitive) to <i>keep</i> (oneself) <i>away</i>, that is, <i>be distant</i> (literally or figuratively): - be, have, receive."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G472\">G472</a>"}]}